# Code blocks

A PHP example:

``` php
<?php
declare(strict_types=1);

function greet(string $name): string {
    return "Hello, {$name}!";
}
```

A JavaScript example:

``` javascript
function greet(name) {
    return `Hello, ${name}!`;
}
```

A bash example:

``` bash
#!/usr/bin/env bash
set -euo pipefail
echo "hello"
```

A YAML example:

``` yaml
name: example
version: 1.0
dependencies:
  - foo
  - bar
```

A raw HTML block:

``` =html
<details><summary>Click</summary>Hidden content</details>
```

Verbatim inline: `printf("%s\n", x);` in the middle of text.
